Summary:

The majority of reviewers found these socks difficult to put on, especially if they had larger than average calves. Many also found that the socks were too tight at the top of the calf, and some even said that the socks cut off circulation. There were also a few reviewers who found the socks too loose at the ankle. However, the majority of reviewers found that the socks were well-made and had good compression.

